---

<Layout
  title="OpenAGI Media — 自媒体矩阵与增长看板"
  description="OpenAGI 自媒体平台账号、粉丝与增长趋势看板。"
>
  <main class="container">
    <header class="hero">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
      <h1>OpenAGI Media</h1>
      <p>OpenAGI 自媒体矩阵、粉丝基线与增长趋势（持续更新）</p>
    </header>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>平台账号与增长情况</h2>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>平台</th>
              <th>账号</th>
              <th>主页</th>
              <th>粉丝</th>
              <th>近7天</th>
              <th>近30天</th>
              <th>更新时间</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {mediaAccounts.map((item) => (
              <tr>
                <td>{item.platform}</td>
                <td>{item.account}</td>
                <td>
                  <a href={item.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">访问</a>
                </td>
                <td>{item.followers}</td>
                <td>{item.delta7d}</td>
                <td>{item.delta30d}</td>
                <td>{item.updatedAt}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="note">注：当前为初始建档版本。后续将接入自动采集或手动周更机制维护粉丝与增长数据。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <h2>增长记录 / 实验日志（GEO Skills 预留）</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>目标：提升 OpenAGI 在开发者社区与中文互联网的可见度与影响力。</li>
        <li>后续动作：接入 ClawHub GEO Skills，按平台执行关键词优化、内容迭代与传播实验。</li>
        <li>指标追踪：曝光、互动率、净增粉、转化到 openagi.ai 的点击。</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="chips">
        <span>OpenAGI.ai</span>
        <span>OpenAGI.foundation</span>
        <span>OpenAGI.bot</span>
        <span>GEO Skills</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--primary-bright), var(--cyan-bright));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
    .back-link { color: var(--primary-bright); text-decoration: none; }

    .panel {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(17, 24, 39, .82), rgba(10, 15, 26, .92));
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .panel h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }

    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; min-width: 900px; }
    th, td { padding: 0.65rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); text-align: left; }
    th { color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 600; }
    td a { color: var(--primary-bright); text-decoration: none; }
    td a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .note { margin-top: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; }

    ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .chips { margin-top: 0.9rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .chips span {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-accent);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
      color: var(--cyan-bright);
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
